{"title":"来自农村的诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":11,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自农村的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新来的社员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张响涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县长来到我庄上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要立户当社员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前晌到庄安锅灶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后晌下地干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县长原是庄稼汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命干了二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今上山当农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南洼犁地甩大鞭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘚儿哦喝，嘚儿哦喝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满头大汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湿透衣衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“县长啊，歇一会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喘喘气儿抽袋烟。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县长笑嘿嘿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是抡大鞭："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“往后不要叫县长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是咱社一社员。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北唐山）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社啊，你不会垮\t牛宝童"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高级社啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富农在毒恶的诅咒：“社要垮”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让他咒骂他自己吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社不垮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如青天不会坍！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送村头牛宝童听说县长走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少送村头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉拉住县长手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当着闺女开了口："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“县长县长您别走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后丰收喝杯酒！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957年，秋天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}